stá reduzida.</p><div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2"><button data-slot="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md font-medium transition-colors outline-none disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] focus-visible:ring-ds-accent/40 active:translate-y-px [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 border border-border-default bg-transparent text-fg hover:bg-bg-surface-hover h-8 px-3 text-xs"><span>Tentar novamente</span></button><button type="button" aria-haspopup="dialog" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="radix-_R_2ps_" data-state="closed" data-slot="dialog-trigger"><button data-slot="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md font-medium transition-colors outline-none disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] focus-visible:ring-ds-accent/40 active:translate-y-px [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 border border-border-default bg-transparent text-fg hover:bg-bg-surface-hover h-8 px-3 text-xs"><span>Ver detalhes</span></button></button><a class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border border-border px-3 py-1.5 text-sm hover:bg-bg-surface-hover" href="mailto:suporte@verifibin.local?subject=Reportar%20degrada%C3%A7%C3%A3o">Reportar</a></div></div><div data-slot="card" class="text-fg flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 border-border bg-card"><div data-slot="card-header" class="@container/card-header grid auto-rows-min grid-rows-[auto_auto] items-start gap-1.5 px-6 has-data-[slot=card-action]:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] [.border-b]:pb-6"><div data-slot="card-title" class="text-fg text-lg font-semibold">Sobre este BIN</div><div data-slot="card-description" class="text-fg-muted text-sm">Resumo textual determinístico com rastreabilidade das afirmações.</div></div><div data-slot="card-content" class="px-6 space-y-3"><p class="text-sm text-fg-muted">O BIN 411111 pertence a Issuer (Estados Unidos), bandeira não informada, cartão tipo não informado. Para uma transação de valor não informado num merchant no país não informado (categoria não informada), o motor identificou Risco médio — análise parcial com base em 1 de 3 fontes confirmadas. A análise é preliminar e pode mudar com novas fontes.</p><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2"><button data-state="closed" data-slot="tooltip-trigger"><span data-slot="badge" class="inline-flex w-fit items-center gap-1 rounded-full px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium bg-transparent text-fg border border-border-default">BIN / emissor</span></button><button data-state="closed" data-slot="tooltip-trigger"><span data-slot="badge" class="inline-flex w-fit items-center gap-1 rounded-full px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium bg-transparent text-fg border border-border-default">Contexto transação</span></button><button data-state="closed" data-slot="tooltip-trigger"><span data-slot="badge" class="inline-flex w-fit items-center gap-1 rounded-full px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium bg-transparent text-fg border border-border-default">Score</span></button></div></div></div><div class="grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-4"><div data-slot="card" class="flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl bg-bg-surface py-6 border border-border text-foreground"><div data-slot="card-header" class="@container/card-header grid auto-rows-min grid-rows-[auto_auto] items-start gap-1.5 px-6 has-data-[slot=card-action]:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] [.border-b]:pb-6"><div data-slot="card-description" class="text-fg-muted text-sm">Score geral</div><div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-2"><div data-slot="card-title" class="text-fg text-2xl font-bold">Risco médio — análise parcial</div><button type="button" aria-haspopup="dialog" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="radix-_R_2ibs_" data-state="closed" data-slot="dialog-trigger"><button data-slot="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md font-medium transition-colors outline-none disabled: