exports[`Premium3DAnalyzer snapshots > motor degradado total 1`] = `"<div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl space-y-6 px-4 py-10 font-sans text-fg"><div class="space-y-2 text-center"><div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-border-subtle bg-bg-surface px-4 py-2 text-sm text-fg-muted"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-zap h-4 w-4 text-ds-accent" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"></path></svg>VeriFiBIN Premium 3.0</div><h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-fg">Motor Holístico Multidimensional</h1><p class="text-sm text-fg-muted">Análise 6D com contexto transacional, múltiplas fontes e explicações em dois modos.</p></div><div data-slot="card" class="text-fg flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border border-border-subtle bg-bg-surface py-6"><div data-slot="card-header" class="@container/card-header grid auto-rows-min grid-rows-[auto_auto] items-start gap-1.5 px-6 has-data-[slot=card-action]:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] [.border-b]:pb-6"><div data-slot="card-title" class="text-fg flex items-center gap-2 text-lg font-semibold"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-earth h-5 w-5 text-ds-accent" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.54 15H17a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4.54"></path><path d="M7 3.34V5a3 3 0 0 0 3 3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2c0 1.1.9 2 2 2a2 2 0 0 0 2-2c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h3.17"></path><path d="M11 21.95V18a2 2 0 0 0-2-2a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-1a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H2.05"></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle></svg>Modo de explicação</div><div data-slot="card-description" class="text-fg-muted text-sm">Explicações curtas e simples para leitura rápida.</div></div><div data-slot="card-content" class="px-6 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row"><div dir="ltr" data-orientation="horizontal" data-slot="tabs" class="flex flex-col gap-3 w-fit"><div role="tablist" aria-orientation="horizontal" data-slot="tabs-list" class="inline-flex w-fit items-center gap-1 border-b border-border-subtle" tabindex="-1" data-orientation="horizontal" style="outline:none"><button type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="radix-_R_i_-content-popular" data-state="active" id="radix-_R_i_-trigger-popular" data-slot="tabs-trigger" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center border-b-2 border-transparent px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-fg-muted transition-colors hover:text-fg focus-visible:rounded-sm focus-visible:ring-[3px] focus-visible:ring-ds-accent/40 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 data-[state=active]:border-ds-accent data-[state=active]:text-fg" tabindex="-1" data-orientation="horizontal" data-radix-collection-item=""><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-users mr-2 h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg>Modo Popular</button><button type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="radix-_R_i_-content-technical" data-state="inactive" id="radix-_R_i_-trigger-technical" data-slot="tabs-trigger" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center border-b-2 border-transparent px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-fg-muted transition-colors hover:text-fg focus-visible:rounded-sm focus-visible:ring-[3px] focus-visible:ring-ds-accent/40 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 data-[state=active]:border-ds-accent data-[state=active]:text-fg" tabindex="-1" data-orientation="horizontal" data-radix-collection-item=""><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-wrench mr-2 h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"></path></svg>Modo Técnico</button></div></div></div></div><div data-slot="card" class="text-fg flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border border-border-subtle bg-bg-surface py-6"><div data-slot="card-header" class="@container/card-header grid auto-rows-min grid-rows-[auto_auto] items-start gap-1.5 px-6 has-data-[slot=card-action]:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] [.border-b]:pb-6"><div data-slot="card-title" class="text-fg text-lg font-semibold">Analisar BIN com contexto</div><div data-slot="card-description" class="text-fg-muted text-sm">Preencha o BIN e, se quiser, complemente com contexto transacional opcional.</div></div><div data-slot="card-content" class="px-6 space-y-4"><div class="grid gap-3 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto]"><input type="text" data-slot="input" class="h-9 w-full min-w-0 rounded-md border border-border-default bg-bg-surface px-3 py-1 text-fg shadow-xs outline-none transition-colors placeholder:text-fg-muted hover:border-border-strong focus-visible:border-ds-accent focus-visible:ring-[3px] focus-visible:ring-ds-accent/40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:border-border-subtle disabled:bg-bg-surface-elevated disabled:text-fg-disabled disabled:opacity-100 file:border-0 file:bg-transparent file:text-sm file:font-medium text-sm" placeholder="BIN (6 a 8 dígitos)" maxLength="8" aria-describedby="bin-validation-message" value=""/><button data-slot="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md font-medium transition-colors outline-none disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] focus-visible:ring-ds-accent/40 active:translate-y-px [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 border border-border-default bg-bg-surface text-fg hover:bg-bg-surface-hover h-9 px-4 text-sm" aria-busy="false"><span>Analisar</span></button></div><p id="bin-validation-message" class="text-xs text-fg-muted">Informe entre 6 e 8 dígitos para análise.</p><div data-state="closed" class="rounded-lg border border-border bg-card/50 p-4"><button type="button" aria-controls="radix-_R_3j_" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed" class="flex w-full items-center justify-between gap-3 text-left text-sm font-medium text-foreground"><span class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-wrench h-4 w-4 text-ds-accent" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"></path></svg>Contexto avançado da transação (opcional — melhora a precisão da análise)</span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down h-4 w-4 text-muted-foreground transition-transform"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></button><div data-state="closed" id="radix-_R_3j_" hidden="" class="mt-4 space-y-4 border-t border-border pt-4"></div></div></div></div><div aria-live="polite"><div class="space-y-6"><div class="sticky top-4 z-20 rounded-lg border border-status-warning/40 bg-status-warning/10 p-4"><p class="text-sm font-medium text-status-warning">⚠️ Análise em modo parcial — 0 de 3 fontes respondeu.</p><p class="mt-1 text-xs text-fg-muted">A precisão dos scores está reduzida.</p><div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2"><button data-slot="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md font-medium transition-colors outline-none disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] focus-visible:ring-ds-accent/40 active:translate-y-px [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 border border-border-default bg-transparent text-fg hover:bg-bg-surface-hover h-8 px-3 text-xs"><span>Tentar novamente</span></button><button type="button" aria-haspopup="dialog" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="radix-_R_2ps_" data-state="closed" data-slot="dialog-trigger"><button data-slot="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md font-medium transition-colors outline-none disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] focus-visible:ring-ds-accent/40 active:translate-y-px [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 border border-border-default bg-transparent text-fg hover:bg-bg-surface-hover h-8 px-3 text-xs"><span>Ver detalhes</span></button></button><a class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border border-border px-3 py-1.5 text-sm hover:bg-bg-surface-hover" href="mailto:suporte@verifibin.local?subject=Reportar%20degrada%C3%A7%C3%A3o">Reportar</a></div></div><div data-slot="card" class="text-fg flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 border-border bg-card"><div data-slot="card-header" class="@container/card-header grid auto-rows-min grid-rows-[auto_auto] items-start gap-1.5 px-6 has-data-[slot=card-action]:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] [.border-b]:pb-6"><div data-slot="card-title" class="text-fg text-lg font-semibold">Sobre este BIN</div><div data-slot="card-description" class="text-fg-muted text-sm">Resumo textual determinístico com rastreabilidade das afirmações.</div></div><div data-slot="card-content" class="px-6 space-y-3"><p class="text-sm text-fg-muted">O BIN 411111 pertence a Issuer (Estados Unidos), bandeira não informada, cartão tipo não informado. Para uma transação de valor não informado num merchant no país não informado (categoria não informada), o motor identificou Indisponível com base em 0 de 3 fontes confirmadas. A análise é preliminar e pode mudar com novas fontes.</p><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2"><button data-state="closed" data-slot="tooltip-trigger"><span data-slot="badge" class="inline-flex w-fit items-center gap-1 rounded-full px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium bg-transparent text-fg border border-border-default">BIN / emissor</span></button><button data-state="closed" data-slot="tooltip-trigger"><span data-slot="badge" class="inline-flex w-fit items-center gap-1 rounded-full px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium bg-transparent text-fg border border-border-default">Contexto transação</span></button><button data-state="closed" data-slot="tooltip-trigger"><span data-slot="badge" class="inline-flex w-fit items-center gap-1 rounded-full px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium bg-transparent text-fg border border-border-default">Score</span></button></div></div></div><div class="grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-4"><div data-slot="card" class="flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl bg-bg-surface py-6 border border-border text-foreground"><div data-slot="card-header" class="@container/card-header grid auto-rows-min grid-rows-[auto_auto] items-start gap-1.5 px-6 has-data-[slot=card-action]:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] [.border-b]:pb-6"><div data-slot="card-description" class="text-fg-muted text-sm">Score geral</div><div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-2"><div data-slot="card-title" class="text-fg text-2xl font-bold">Indisponível</div><button type="button" aria-haspopup="dialog" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="radix-_R_2ibs_" data-state="closed" data-slot="dialog-trigger"><button data-slot="button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md font-medium transition-colors outline-none disabled:pointer-events-none disabled